    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "t41",
      "x": 76,
      "y": 938,
      "text": "TEMPORAL PLATFORM  (Generic Job Framework + Web Dashboard)\n\nInstrument Master Sync (6 PM)  |  Corporate Actions (8 PM)  |  Pre-Market Loading (7:35 AM)  |  EOD Reconciliation (post-close)\nExpiry Day Cleanup (Thu 3:30 PM)  |  Candle Archival (weekly)  |  NAV Update (11 PM)  |  Historical Data Migration (one-time)\n+ Any custom workflow created by any team via Temporal Dashboard (search / retry / cancel / inspect history)",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#f08c00"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "t42",
      "x": 690,
      "y": 1072,
      "text": "DATA STORES",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e"
    },
    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "r43",
      "x": 110,
      "y": 1102,
      "width": 240,
      "height": 126,
